{"tid":1599033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"等淺黃港豬藍絲唔好再發大中華膠夢文宣","createTime":"2019-09-27T18:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T18:04:40.000Z","uid":143564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"55a2f7832c88463b37f488fead78439e5f8670ab","tid":1599033,"uid":143564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"有人話唔好參與林鄭對話會 唔好俾佢營造大台 俾佢爭取主導權 我覺得就算黃絲唔去 藍絲都會去 如果咁多藍絲做宣傳 擔心會令淺黃轉藍 我覺得所謂既對話會 目標唔係要同條柒婆對話 要係要同埋淺黃 港豬 淺藍解釋香港實際狀況 而家邊個係妹仔邊個係主人 而唔使再發大中華膠夢 即使唔係對話會講 都可以平時街上面既文宣貼出黎 或者民間記者會講下都好<br />\n<br />\n論點如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港直接投資同海外集資佔大陸重要經濟比例 <br />\n<br />\n2.香港有國際金融中心地位 係因為有可信賴既法制 同營商環境 上海都取代唔到 反送中令其他國家信你唔過＝玩完<br />\n<br />\nRef:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%99%B8%E4%B9%8B%E9%96%93%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E5%AE%B3%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258D%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%258D%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2589%2596%25E6%259E%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2599%25B8%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=5d102ff5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258D%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%258D%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2589%2596%25E6%259E%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2599%25B8%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2